rows.label: qst701915_msg0002
rows.name:
Maybe I'll eat before we
set off for Invidia.

rows.label: qst701915_msg0101
rows.name: Why did you pick me as leader?

rows.label: qst701915_msg0102
rows.name:
I mean, sure, as a representative of
the resistance army, I'll probably
do a bang-up job of it.

rows.label: qst701915_msg0103
rows.name:
But I'll be so busy I doubt I'll have
time to sample any Invidian foods.

rows.label: qst701915_msg0201
rows.name:
I'm stoked that the mission's over.
Time to go put my feet up, sip on
a cold brew and fill up the ol' tum.

rows.label: qst701915_msg0202
rows.name:
Or I would, if our exalted Lieutenant
Veronica wasn't giving me the evil eye.

rows.label: qst701915_msg0203
rows.name:
I knew this'd happen... I ought to have
had my fill of Puran in Fons Maim,
at least, but now that ship's sailed...
